66
00:06:35,090 --> 00:06:35,909
Darling.

67
00:06:36,630 --> 00:06:38,590
Don't talk so distantly.

68
00:06:38,610 --> 00:06:40,740
Although I'm the daughter of the Duke,

69
00:06:40,790 --> 00:06:42,120
since I've married you,

70
