73
00:07:01,300 --> 00:07:02,220
Darling.

74
00:07:02,960 --> 00:07:04,440
Listen to me.

75
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:12,270
Darling, listen to me.

76
00:07:12,390 --> 00:07:13,630
Well, I...

77
00:07:13,630 --> 00:07:15,030
Are you looking for this?

78
00:07:17,840 --> 00:07:18,790
Are you going to live a good life

79
00:07:18,790 --> 00:07:20,720
with me with the help of this thing?

80
00:07:29,410 --> 00:07:30,850
I was thinking that

81
00:07:31,590 --> 00:07:33,230
in our wedding today,

82
00:07:33,960 --> 00:07:35,710
if you walk out of this room,

83
00:07:36,030 --> 00:07:37,890
it would be such a disgrace for me.

84
00:07:38,260 --> 00:07:40,520
If you really walk out of this room today,

85
00:07:41,760 --> 00:07:42,630
I'll kill myself.

86
00:07:42,630 --> 00:07:43,550
What are you doing?

87
00:07:43,550 --> 00:07:44,550
Give me the knife.

88
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:46,240
If you walk out of this room today,

89
00:07:46,240 --> 00:07:47,240
I'll kill myself.

90
00:07:47,950 --> 00:07:49,030
Put down the knife.

91
00:07:51,860 --> 00:07:54,390
What should I do to make you put down the knife?

92
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:56,040
Promise me that

93
00:07:56,280 --> 00:07:57,610
you'll stay here today.

94
00:07:59,450 --> 00:08:01,170
Okay. I promise you.

95
00:08:01,200 --> 00:08:02,460
Put the knife down now.

96
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:04,980
Hurry up.

97
00:08:12,550 --> 00:08:13,240
Miss Su.

98
00:08:13,670 --> 00:08:14,230
Actually...

99
00:08:14,230 --> 00:08:14,830
Darling.

100
00:08:16,430 --> 00:08:17,690
What are you doing?

101
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:19,560
It's the wedding night.

102
00:08:19,780 --> 00:08:21,310
What do you think I'm doing?

103
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:28,620
What else can I do?

104
00:08:28,830 --> 00:08:31,750
-Miss Su, what are you doing?
-Of course I'm helping you change your clothes.

105
00:08:31,750 --> 00:08:33,309
I have something to tell you.

106
00:08:33,309 --> 00:08:34,710
Just tell me after you finish changing your clothes.

107
00:08:34,710 --> 00:08:36,280
-No.
-It won't be too late then.

108
00:08:36,280 --> 00:08:37,480
I can't live anymore.

109
00:08:41,190 --> 00:08:41,870
What?

110
00:08:49,730 --> 00:08:51,530
Actually, I have tuberculosis.

111
00:08:52,350 --> 00:08:54,410
The doctor said that I would die soon.

112
00:08:55,600 --> 00:08:57,730
I really don't want to waste your time.

113
00:09:08,830 --> 00:09:09,510
Really?

114
00:09:12,310 --> 00:09:12,990
Yes.

115
00:09:19,340 --> 00:09:21,470
I really don't want to waste your time.

116
00:09:26,560 --> 00:09:27,420
It's all right.

117
00:09:28,110 --> 00:09:29,950
Since I've married you,

118
00:09:30,130 --> 00:09:31,730
I'm a member of the Xu Family.

119
00:09:32,910 --> 00:09:34,380
If you die,

120
00:09:34,670 --> 00:09:36,400
I will take care of them for you.

121
00:09:38,360 --> 00:09:40,470
Using Blood-generating Pills is just an outdated trick.

122
00:09:40,470 --> 00:09:41,470
No, Miss Su.

123
00:09:41,490 --> 00:09:42,970
It's clean now. It's fine.

124
00:09:44,310 --> 00:09:45,550
But Miss Su, you...

125
00:09:49,600 --> 00:09:50,680
What are you doing?

126
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:52,150
Of course I'm helping you change your clothes.

127
00:09:52,150 --> 00:09:52,950
Don't move.

128
00:09:53,710 --> 00:09:54,220
No.

129
00:09:56,560 --> 00:09:57,530
Don't move.

130
00:09:57,370 --> 00:09:59,960
[Wedding]

131
00:09:58,320 --> 00:09:59,230
Honey.

132
00:10:00,010 --> 00:10:00,940
Don't do this.

133
00:10:01,070 --> 00:10:01,670
Don't move.

134
00:10:01,670 --> 00:10:02,430
What are you doing?

135
00:10:02,430 --> 00:10:03,390
It looks like

136
00:10:03,470 --> 00:10:06,350
they don't have time to eat my ginseng fruits.

137
00:10:06,400 --> 00:10:07,390
Take off this one, too. Hurry up.

138
00:10:07,390 --> 00:10:07,990
Honey.

139
00:10:11,650 --> 00:10:13,860
It's neither in the room nor with him.

140
00:10:14,880 --> 00:10:17,670
It seems that it's necessary to discuss and think about this thing more carefully.

141
00:10:17,670 --> 00:10:19,080
This is strange.

142
00:10:19,170 --> 00:10:21,100
I searched his whole body just now.

143
00:10:29,910 --> 00:10:31,190
I'm a bit hungry.

144
00:10:31,830 --> 00:10:33,360
I'm going to eat something.

145
00:10:52,840 --> 00:10:54,520
What's inside?

146
00:10:54,870 --> 00:10:55,650
Sweet dumplings.

147
00:10:55,650 --> 00:10:56,930
They're fermented with wine.

148
00:10:56,930 --> 00:10:57,520
Wine?

149
00:10:59,880 --> 00:11:01,770
But I can't drink wine.

150
00:11:14,760 --> 00:11:23,140
[Wedding]

151
00:11:27,070 --> 00:11:27,760
My Lord,

152
00:11:28,270 --> 00:11:30,150
later when Xu Muchen comes here,

153
00:11:30,150 --> 00:11:31,760
I'm afraid he might trick us.

154
00:11:34,830 --> 00:11:37,470
Without his position in the Zichen Department,

155
00:11:37,470 --> 00:11:39,330
he would be just a commoner.

156
00:11:39,710 --> 00:11:41,670
If he dares to make trouble with us,

157
00:11:42,870 --> 00:11:45,490
you can ask your buddies whom you've summoned here

158
00:11:45,490 --> 00:11:47,420
to beat him up to make him disabled.

159
00:11:47,810 --> 00:11:48,410
Yes.

160
00:12:03,090 --> 00:12:03,940
My Lord.

161
00:12:06,380 --> 00:12:07,340
Xu Muchen.

162
00:12:07,980 --> 00:12:16,340
[Written Evidence]

163
00:12:08,780 --> 00:12:09,650
This is

164
00:12:09,830 --> 00:12:13,430
the written evidence for the jade I've bought from Scholar Lyu.

165
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:16,700
Where is my gold inlaid with jade?

166
00:12:25,270 --> 00:12:26,200
What do you mean?

167
00:12:26,530 --> 00:12:27,530
I'll pay 200 taels

168
00:12:28,430 --> 00:12:30,360
to redeem the jade for Scholar Lyu.

169
00:12:30,400 --> 00:12:32,720
My gold inlaid with jade is worth 10,000 taels in the market.

170
00:12:32,720 --> 00:12:35,220
You want to give me 200 taels to redeem it from me?

171
00:12:35,220 --> 00:12:37,220
You also paid only 200 taels to buy it

172
00:12:37,590 --> 00:12:39,250
from Scholar Lyu, didn't you?

173
00:12:44,270 --> 00:12:46,070
Xu Muchen, it's none of your business!

174
00:12:46,070 --> 00:12:48,350
You took advantage of his difficult situation and forced him to sell it to you at a low price.

175
00:12:48,350 --> 00:12:50,750
I'll definitely intervene in this matter.

176
00:12:50,830 --> 00:12:52,920
You can help Scholar Lyu once,

177
00:12:52,950 --> 00:12:54,790
but there are times when you can't pay attention to him.

178
00:12:54,790 --> 00:12:56,920
He's just a poor and pedantic scholar.

179
00:12:57,190 --> 00:12:59,650
Do you think I dare not make trouble with him?

180
00:12:59,710 --> 00:13:00,390
Beat him!

181
00:13:00,710 --> 00:13:02,640
Beat him until he spit out the jade.

182
00:13:08,830 --> 00:13:09,420
Alright.

183
00:13:10,870 --> 00:13:13,330
Then I'll beat you until you dare not do that.

184
00:14:16,500 --> 00:14:17,670
What do you want to do?

185
00:14:17,670 --> 00:14:18,620
Let me tell you.

186
00:14:18,620 --> 00:14:20,630
Lord Gongyang of the Ministry of Justice is my nephew.

187
00:14:20,630 --> 00:14:21,830
If you dare to hit me,

188
00:14:21,830 --> 00:14:23,830
I'll teach you a lesson.

189
00:15:13,470 --> 00:15:15,790
[Xu's Mansion]

190
00:15:15,800 --> 00:15:18,240
[Wedding]

191
00:15:41,390 --> 00:15:42,800
Have Young Master and Young Madam got up?

192
00:15:42,800 --> 00:15:44,910
Old Madam has been waiting for so long that she's impatient now.

193
00:15:44,910 --> 00:15:45,870
I don't know.

194
00:15:46,070 --> 00:15:47,600
I dare not ask them to get up.

195
00:15:47,900 --> 00:15:48,910
Are you afraid of Young Master

196
00:15:48,910 --> 00:15:50,150
or Old Madam?

197
00:15:51,070 --> 00:15:51,750
I...

198
00:15:52,390 --> 00:15:53,080
But...

199
00:15:53,270 --> 00:15:53,990
We've got up.

200
00:15:53,990 --> 00:15:55,190
We'll be right there.

201
00:15:59,340 --> 00:16:00,510
Let's wash up quickly.

202
00:16:00,510 --> 00:16:01,970
My mother has a bad temper.

203
00:16:22,150 --> 00:16:23,070
Wait. Wait.

204
00:16:23,150 --> 00:16:23,630
They're entangled together.

205
00:16:23,630 --> 00:16:24,350
Let me do it.

206
00:16:24,380 --> 00:16:25,270
Don't move. Don't move.

207
00:16:25,270 --> 00:16:25,930
Don't move.

208
00:16:26,090 --> 00:16:27,320
You made my hair entangled with yours.

209
00:16:27,320 --> 00:16:28,190
Don't move.

210
00:16:29,830 --> 00:16:30,590
Don't move.

211
00:16:32,640 --> 00:16:33,370
Are you done?

212
00:16:35,580 --> 00:16:36,300
Yes.

213
00:17:17,680 --> 00:17:24,220
[Peaceful Residence]

214
00:17:30,110 --> 00:17:33,520
[Wedding]

215
00:17:30,990 --> 00:17:31,990
This way, please.

216
00:17:47,510 --> 00:17:49,040
Young Master, Young Madam.

217
00:17:54,350 --> 00:17:58,340
[Wedding]

218
00:17:54,870 --> 00:17:55,510
Xiao Qiu.

219
00:17:55,650 --> 00:17:57,200
Did you really hear everything?

220
00:17:57,200 --> 00:17:59,110
Yes, I heard everything.

221
00:17:59,840 --> 00:18:01,080
Did they really...

222
00:18:02,320 --> 00:18:04,400
Old Madam, just stop asking me.

223
00:18:04,470 --> 00:18:06,030
I feel embarrassed.

224
00:18:06,380 --> 00:18:07,780
Though your Young Master

225
00:18:07,840 --> 00:18:09,920
always looks cool and indifferent,

226
00:18:09,950 --> 00:18:10,940
I don't have to

227
00:18:11,110 --> 00:18:12,910
worry about such things for him.

228
00:18:15,800 --> 00:18:16,410
Mother.

229
00:18:17,200 --> 00:18:18,990
If newlyweds get up so late,

230
00:18:18,990 --> 00:18:20,450
people will laugh at them.

231
00:18:20,910 --> 00:18:21,510
Yes.

232
00:18:21,670 --> 00:18:22,550
I'm sorry.

233
00:18:25,570 --> 00:18:26,650
I'm sorry, too.

234
00:18:26,830 --> 00:18:28,290
Please punish me, Mother.

235
00:18:29,910 --> 00:18:31,990
Zhen, what are you talking about?

236
00:18:32,370 --> 00:18:34,110
Don't stand there. Sit down.

237
00:18:57,960 --> 00:18:58,510
Mother.

238
00:18:58,700 --> 00:18:59,380
Please eat.

239
00:19:01,780 --> 00:19:03,110
Zhen, no need to stand on ceremony.

240
00:19:03,110 --> 00:19:04,120
Eat more.

241
00:19:21,030 --> 00:19:23,310
She's trying to display her power over me.

242
00:19:23,310 --> 00:19:24,890
Luckily, I was the one who came here.

243
00:19:24,890 --> 00:19:26,280
If Jinzhen had been the one sitting here,

244
00:19:26,280 --> 00:19:27,390
she would have been bullied by this woman

245
00:19:27,390 --> 00:19:28,650
and her son miserably.

246
00:19:28,800 --> 00:19:30,160
Mrs. Liu's son was really

247
00:19:30,160 --> 00:19:31,440
rude yesterday.

248
00:19:31,460 --> 00:19:32,700
On your wedding day,

249
00:19:32,730 --> 00:19:34,390
he even stood up to eat the food.

250
00:19:34,390 --> 00:19:35,990
What a laughing stock he was.

251
00:19:37,060 --> 00:19:38,320
Mother, you're right.

252
00:19:46,010 --> 00:19:47,660
How come my hairpin is missing?

253
00:19:47,410 --> 00:19:52,920
[Wedding]

254
00:19:48,220 --> 00:19:50,350
Did it fall into the parterre outside?

255
00:19:50,830 --> 00:19:51,470
Chen,

256
00:19:51,520 --> 00:19:52,980
help me look for it at once.

257
00:19:53,320 --> 00:19:54,040
I'll go.

258
00:19:54,290 --> 00:19:55,670
[Wedding]

259
00:19:54,590 --> 00:19:55,790
The parterre, right?

260
00:19:59,860 --> 00:20:06,510
[Wedding]

261
00:20:17,080 --> 00:20:17,720
Mother.

262
00:20:18,190 --> 00:20:19,720
Which hairpin did you lose?

263
00:20:19,980 --> 00:20:21,520
It's the one made of gold inlaid with jade,

264
00:20:21,520 --> 00:20:23,320
and there are coral stones on it.

265
00:20:25,550 --> 00:20:27,350
You mean the one you always wore?

266
00:20:27,790 --> 00:20:28,670
Yes, that's it.

267
00:20:29,890 --> 00:20:31,220
It's right on your head.

268
00:20:39,510 --> 00:20:41,230
Zhen, come back.

269
00:20:41,230 --> 00:20:42,030
Stop looking for it.

270
00:20:42,030 --> 00:20:42,950
What's wrong?

271
00:20:42,820 --> 00:20:47,540
[Wedding]

272
00:20:42,950 --> 00:20:44,150
I'm so forgetful.

273
00:20:44,310 --> 00:20:46,230
This hairpin is right on my head.

274
00:20:46,430 --> 00:20:47,830
Come here and have a rest.

275
00:20:49,230 --> 00:20:51,440
This annoying old woman played tricks on me deliberately.

276
00:20:51,440 --> 00:20:52,040
Coming.

277
00:20:52,650 --> 00:20:59,840
[Wedding]

278
00:21:02,320 --> 00:21:03,390
Thanks for your hard work.

279
00:21:03,390 --> 00:21:04,230
Have some tea.

280
00:21:05,820 --> 00:21:09,090
This is the good tea which is stored like treasure in our mansion.

281
00:21:09,090 --> 00:21:10,430
Unfortunately, in order to wait for you,

282
00:21:10,430 --> 00:21:12,150
the hot tea has become cold.

283
00:21:12,180 --> 00:21:13,360
Just don't drink it.

284
00:21:13,680 --> 00:21:15,210
I'll ask someone to dump it.

285
00:21:16,990 --> 00:21:18,390
It'll be a pity to dump it.

286
00:21:18,400 --> 00:21:19,060
How about this?

287
00:21:19,060 --> 00:21:22,270
[Wedding]

288
00:21:19,210 --> 00:21:20,340
I'll figure out a way

289
00:21:20,370 --> 00:21:21,510
to turn the tea into a delicious dish.

290
00:21:21,510 --> 00:21:22,710
Then you can taste it.

291
00:21:46,990 --> 00:21:48,590
Let me taste it for you first.

292
00:21:58,300 --> 00:22:00,150
What kind of strange method is this?

293
00:22:00,150 --> 00:22:01,210
Does it taste good?

294
00:22:01,220 --> 00:22:02,420
I'll let you taste it.

295
00:22:20,030 --> 00:22:20,670
How is it?

296
00:22:22,300 --> 00:22:23,620
This tastes

297
00:22:23,820 --> 00:22:24,500
just so-so.

298
00:22:24,520 --> 00:22:25,750
But the weather is so hot,

299
00:22:25,750 --> 00:22:27,070
and I'm very thirsty, too.

300
00:22:27,070 --> 00:22:28,470
I'll just make do with it.

301
00:22:30,810 --> 00:22:31,360
Mother,

302
00:22:32,040 --> 00:22:33,270
if you are really thirsty,

303
00:22:33,270 --> 00:22:34,580
I'll get you a cup of plain boiled water.

304
00:22:34,480 --> 00:22:39,730
[Wedding]

305
00:22:34,930 --> 00:22:36,340
Don't get me a cup of plain boiled water.

306
00:22:36,340 --> 00:22:37,960
Can plain boiled water help to relieve summer-heat?

307
00:22:37,960 --> 00:22:39,160
Give me one more cup of this.

308
00:22:39,160 --> 00:22:39,710
Okay.

309
00:22:48,230 --> 00:22:49,760
Old Madam, the soup is here.

310
00:22:50,670 --> 00:22:51,750
Let me do it.

311
00:22:51,890 --> 00:22:53,490
Just let them ladle the soup.

312
00:22:53,750 --> 00:22:54,480
It's okay.

313
00:22:54,750 --> 00:22:56,590
I lost my mother when I was a child.

314
00:22:56,590 --> 00:22:58,490
I don't know how it feels to be loved

315
00:22:58,490 --> 00:22:59,440
by a mother.

316
00:22:59,560 --> 00:23:00,730
Since I've married into the Xu Family,

317
00:23:00,730 --> 00:23:02,630
I'll regard you as my own mother.

318
00:23:02,910 --> 00:23:04,610
Isn't it my duty to ladle soup

319
00:23:04,630 --> 00:23:05,750
for my own mother?

320
00:23:19,060 --> 00:23:21,620
I tried to make things difficult for Jinzhen again and again,

321
00:23:21,620 --> 00:23:23,380
but she is still so kind.

322
00:23:23,950 --> 00:23:25,070
I was worried that with her identity as the daughter of the Duke,

323
00:23:25,070 --> 00:23:27,430
she would make things difficult for Chen,

324
00:23:28,070 --> 00:23:30,250
but it seems that I've thought too much.

325
00:23:30,250 --> 00:23:30,990
Zhen.

326
00:23:30,990 --> 00:23:31,990
Don't sit there to eat.

327
00:23:31,990 --> 00:23:33,310
Come on. Sit here.

328
00:23:35,070 --> 00:23:36,230
It's okay to sit far away.

329
00:23:36,230 --> 00:23:37,760
It's not good if I break the rules.

330
00:23:37,700 --> 00:23:41,070
[Wedding]

331
00:23:37,840 --> 00:23:39,190
Rules are set by people.

332
00:23:40,080 --> 00:23:41,440
Xiao Dong, Xiao Qiu, come on.

333
00:23:41,440 --> 00:23:41,990
Coming.

334
00:23:44,480 --> 00:23:45,030
Hurry up.

335
00:23:49,970 --> 00:23:51,230
Come on. Come here now.

336
00:23:54,770 --> 00:23:55,910
Eat more.

337
00:23:54,960 --> 00:23:58,060
[Wedding]

338
00:23:55,950 --> 00:23:56,550
Okay.

339
00:24:02,220 --> 00:24:03,000
Mother.

340
00:24:03,350 --> 00:24:04,320
I've finished eating.

341
00:24:04,320 --> 00:24:05,840
I'll go to the study room to fetch something.

342
00:24:05,840 --> 00:24:06,720
Just go.

343
00:24:10,510 --> 00:24:11,520
The study room?

344
00:24:11,740 --> 00:24:14,140
Is the jade pendant hidden in the study room?

345
00:24:14,140 --> 00:24:14,900
Mother.

346
00:24:14,920 --> 00:24:16,450
I'll go serve my husband first.

347
00:24:16,210 --> 00:24:24,200
[Wedding]

348
00:24:16,480 --> 00:24:17,460
Why do you care about him?

349
00:24:17,460 --> 00:24:18,560
Just enjoy your meal.

350
00:24:18,560 --> 00:24:19,750
I've just married him.

351
00:24:19,750 --> 00:24:21,080
It's my duty to serve him.

352
00:24:21,080 --> 00:24:22,210
I'll get going then.

353
00:24:28,200 --> 00:24:29,230
I was thinking that

354
00:24:29,230 --> 00:24:31,200
after the daughter of the Duke married into our family,

355
00:24:31,200 --> 00:24:34,610
[Wedding]

356
00:24:31,270 --> 00:24:32,600
she might give my son and me

357
00:24:32,600 --> 00:24:33,950
a hard time.

358
00:24:34,310 --> 00:24:36,310
It seems that I've worried too much.

359
00:24:36,390 --> 00:24:37,000
Yes.

360
00:24:37,150 --> 00:24:39,150
I think Young Madam is a good person.

361
00:24:39,230 --> 00:24:40,390
But Young Master

362
00:24:40,490 --> 00:24:41,730
is a bit inflexible.

363
00:24:42,480 --> 00:24:45,200
Your Young Master is not someone you can count on now.

364
00:24:45,200 --> 00:24:45,790
From now on,

365
00:24:45,790 --> 00:24:48,070
just get closer to your Young Madam.

366
00:24:48,110 --> 00:24:49,240
Yes, Your Ladyship.

367
00:25:17,380 --> 00:25:18,440
What's the matter?

368
00:25:18,680 --> 00:25:20,150
I'm here to serve you while you're going out.

369
00:25:20,150 --> 00:25:21,410
Don't bother, Miss Su.

370
00:25:27,360 --> 00:25:29,120
Is there anything extraordinary about him?

371
00:25:29,120 --> 00:25:30,330
When I get the jade pendant,

372
00:25:30,330 --> 00:25:32,530
just see how I'll teach you a lesson, Xu.

373
00:26:08,030 --> 00:26:10,430
How come it isn't in the study room, either?

374
00:26:16,750 --> 00:26:17,470
Young Madam.

375
00:26:17,470 --> 00:26:18,530
What are you doing?

376
00:26:20,610 --> 00:26:23,060
I want to clean this room.

377
00:26:23,140 --> 00:26:24,320
You don't have to clean this room.

378
00:26:24,320 --> 00:26:26,030
I clean this place every day.

379
00:26:27,730 --> 00:26:29,000
Well...

380
00:26:29,790 --> 00:26:30,750
I just want to see if there are

381
00:26:30,750 --> 00:26:33,350
any areas you're not able to clean thoroughly.

382
00:26:34,230 --> 00:26:34,830
Look.

383
00:26:34,980 --> 00:26:36,110
It's not clean here.

384
00:26:38,880 --> 00:26:40,210
I'm sorry, Young Madam.

385
00:26:40,550 --> 00:26:42,250
I'll be more careful next time.

386
00:26:42,250 --> 00:26:43,310
And the part inside it, too.

387
00:26:43,310 --> 00:26:44,110
Okay.

388
00:26:44,870 --> 00:26:45,540
Young Madam,

389
00:26:45,540 --> 00:26:47,200
please don't tell Old Madam about it.

390
00:26:47,200 --> 00:26:49,060
She will punish us if she knows it.

391
00:26:50,860 --> 00:26:51,690
Xiao Qiu.

392
00:26:51,980 --> 00:26:53,800
How about I give you a chance to make up for your mistakes?

393
00:26:53,800 --> 00:26:54,310
Okay.

394
00:26:54,340 --> 00:26:55,730
I've been bored since I married into

395
00:26:55,730 --> 00:26:56,860
this family anyway.

396
00:26:56,870 --> 00:26:57,740
Why don't you tell me the secrets

397
00:26:57,740 --> 00:27:00,000
and interesting things in this mansion?

398
00:27:00,440 --> 00:27:01,450
No, Young Madam.

399
00:27:01,480 --> 00:27:05,680
I've always been the most prudent person in keeping secrets in the mansion.

400
00:27:07,140 --> 00:27:09,750
[Zichen Department]

401
00:27:08,230 --> 00:27:08,710
Are you going out?

402
00:27:08,710 --> 00:27:09,150
Yes.

403
00:27:21,910 --> 00:27:22,550
Wu Zhao!

404
00:27:22,920 --> 00:27:23,520
Wu Zhao!

405
00:27:26,010 --> 00:27:27,410
My Lord, why are you here?

406
00:27:27,550 --> 00:27:29,560
Lord Gu let you take the marriage leave for three days, didn't he?

407
00:27:29,560 --> 00:27:30,970
Where is my official uniform?

408
00:27:30,970 --> 00:27:31,830
I've washed it.

409
00:27:32,070 --> 00:27:33,130
Who asked you to wash it?

410
00:27:33,130 --> 00:27:34,330
I asked him to wash it.

411
00:27:37,520 --> 00:27:39,180
I asked him to wash it. So what?

412
00:27:39,870 --> 00:27:40,530
You asked him to wash it?

413
00:27:40,530 --> 00:27:41,580
You should have told me about it first.

414
00:27:41,580 --> 00:27:42,380
Muchen.

415
00:27:42,650 --> 00:27:44,750
I gave you three days of marriage leave.

416
00:27:44,750 --> 00:27:46,280
Why did you come back to work

417
00:27:46,310 --> 00:27:47,750
after just one night?

418
00:27:47,840 --> 00:27:49,650
What will Miss Su think about this?

419
00:27:49,650 --> 00:27:51,470
How can you live with each other in the future?

420
00:27:51,470 --> 00:27:52,670
Muchen.

421
00:27:52,870 --> 00:27:54,720
This is your marriage, and it's very important.

422
00:27:54,720 --> 00:27:56,770
You should go back early

423
00:27:56,780 --> 00:27:58,840
and keep your newlywed wife company.

424
00:27:59,000 --> 00:28:00,130
It's very important

425
00:28:00,160 --> 00:28:01,290
to keep her company.

426
00:28:01,870 --> 00:28:02,510
Hurry up.

427
00:28:02,530 --> 00:28:03,320
Pack up your things now.

428
00:28:03,320 --> 00:28:04,180
Go back at once.

429
00:28:05,630 --> 00:28:07,150
Don't let me see you again.

430
00:28:09,150 --> 00:28:10,080
Get back to work.

431
00:28:12,470 --> 00:28:13,260
You know what?

432
00:28:13,260 --> 00:28:15,180
Old Madam likes eating sweet food the most.

433
00:28:15,180 --> 00:28:16,590
But Young Master doesn't allow her to eat it.

434
00:28:16,590 --> 00:28:17,870
He said it's bad for her health

435
00:28:17,870 --> 00:28:18,870
as she's old now,

436
00:28:19,150 --> 00:28:21,150
so she secretly hid a big box of mille-feuille

437
00:28:21,150 --> 00:28:23,750
under her bed behind Young Master's back.

438
00:28:24,730 --> 00:28:25,640
Young Madam.

439
00:28:25,790 --> 00:28:27,310
Even Ms. Xiao Dong doesn't know about this.

440
00:28:27,310 --> 00:28:28,840
Don't tell others about it.

441
00:28:32,840 --> 00:28:33,670
Normally, we servants

442
00:28:33,670 --> 00:28:35,510
can't eat these snacks.

443
00:28:35,570 --> 00:28:37,910
Young Madam, you're so nice to me.

444
00:28:37,930 --> 00:28:39,430
What are you talking about?

445
00:28:39,430 --> 00:28:41,030
We'll be sisters from now on.

446
00:28:41,440 --> 00:28:42,570
By the way, Xiao Qiu,

447
00:28:42,620 --> 00:28:44,480
have you served my mother-in-law

448
00:28:44,480 --> 00:28:45,670
by her side all the time previously?

449
00:28:45,670 --> 00:28:46,240
Yes.

450
00:28:47,830 --> 00:28:49,330
Ms. Xiao Dong is the leading maid.

451
00:28:49,330 --> 00:28:51,270
She's in charge of everything in the mansion.

452
00:28:51,270 --> 00:28:52,670
I'm the one serving Young Master

453
00:28:52,670 --> 00:28:53,510
and Old Madam.

454
00:28:55,190 --> 00:28:57,520
For all these years, is there any treasure

455
00:28:57,620 --> 00:29:00,120
which my mother-in-law has cherished so much?

456
00:29:00,120 --> 00:29:01,230
For example,

457
00:29:04,390 --> 00:29:06,120
something like a jade pendant.

458
00:29:07,360 --> 00:29:09,290
Old Madam likes hairpins the most.

459
00:29:10,100 --> 00:29:11,950
It's rare to see her wear a jade pendant.

460
00:29:11,950 --> 00:29:13,820
The only mutton-fat jade pendant she has

461
00:29:13,820 --> 00:29:14,950
is very ordinary.

462
00:29:14,950 --> 00:29:16,190
It's not a treasure.

463
00:29:19,030 --> 00:29:21,540
My master didn't say whether it was good jade or not.

464
00:29:21,540 --> 00:29:23,270
I might as well investigate it.

465
00:29:23,510 --> 00:29:24,220
I've heard that

466
00:29:24,220 --> 00:29:26,260
the old Mrs. Xu used to be a princess,

467
00:29:26,340 --> 00:29:28,750
so Xu's Mansion used to be an imperial residence.

468
00:29:28,750 --> 00:29:30,550
Can you show me around?

469
00:29:30,940 --> 00:29:31,740
No problem.

470
00:29:31,760 --> 00:29:33,560
Just tell me where you want to go.

471
00:29:41,350 --> 00:29:43,810
Is there any mysterious place in Xu's Mansion,

472
00:29:43,810 --> 00:29:46,010
which they don't allow others to enter?

473
00:29:46,640 --> 00:29:48,210
A mysterious place?

474
00:29:48,560 --> 00:29:50,950
Isn't that the description in a storybook?

475
00:29:50,950 --> 00:29:53,470
The more mysterious a place is, the more likely it is to have treasures.

476
00:29:53,470 --> 00:29:55,080
Things like elixirs

477
00:29:55,150 --> 00:29:57,050
and secret martial arts books are all hidden inside.

478
00:29:57,050 --> 00:29:59,160
As Xu's Mansion used to be an imperial residence,

479
00:29:59,160 --> 00:30:01,560
do you think there is any secret mechanism here?

480
00:30:01,560 --> 00:30:02,550
Mechanism?

481
00:30:04,750 --> 00:30:05,700
I know.

482
00:30:05,730 --> 00:30:06,670
It's the ancestral hall.

483
00:30:06,670 --> 00:30:07,440
The ancestral hall?

484
00:30:07,440 --> 00:30:08,080
Yes.

485
00:30:08,370 --> 00:30:09,840
The ancestral hall in Xu's Mansion

486
00:30:09,840 --> 00:30:11,540
is cleaned by Young Master himself.

487
00:30:11,540 --> 00:30:14,470
Normally, other people are not allowed to go inside.

488
00:30:15,310 --> 00:30:17,110
Then take me there to have a look.

489
00:30:18,030 --> 00:30:19,030
No.

490
00:30:19,150 --> 00:30:21,750
If Old Madam and Young Master find out about it,

491
00:30:22,110 --> 00:30:23,270
they will punish me.

492
00:30:24,350 --> 00:30:26,390
Ms. Xiao Dong once accidentally went into the ancestral hall when she was a child,

493
00:30:26,390 --> 00:30:27,730
which made Old Madam so angry.

494
00:30:27,730 --> 00:30:30,190
She was locked in the ancestral hall for a whole night as the punishment.

495
00:30:30,190 --> 00:30:31,470
When she came out...

496
00:30:31,540 --> 00:30:32,770
That place is hidden so deeply.

497
00:30:32,770 --> 00:30:34,480
The jade pendant must be there.

498
00:30:34,480 --> 00:30:36,090
What happened when she came out?

499
00:30:36,090 --> 00:30:38,540
She was starving when she came out.

500
00:30:38,570 --> 00:30:40,350
Old Madam felt so worried about her that

501
00:30:40,350 --> 00:30:41,990
she cooked noodles for her personally.

502
00:30:41,990 --> 00:30:42,790
Don't worry.

503
00:30:42,840 --> 00:30:44,000
If we get caught,

504
00:30:44,030 --> 00:30:45,290
I won't let you starve.

505
00:30:59,940 --> 00:31:00,540
This way.

506
00:31:09,690 --> 00:31:13,450
[Inherit the Traditional Virtues]

507
00:31:10,390 --> 00:31:11,150
Young Madam.

508
00:31:11,370 --> 00:31:12,900
This is the ancestral hall.

509
00:31:14,510 --> 00:31:15,270
Xiao Qiu.

510
00:31:15,460 --> 00:31:16,590
Go guard the entrance for me.

511
00:31:16,590 --> 00:31:17,440
Don't let others come inside.

512
00:31:17,440 --> 00:31:18,780
I'll come out after taking a look.

513
00:31:18,780 --> 00:31:19,700
Young Madam.

514
00:31:19,990 --> 00:31:21,190
You really can't go inside.

515
00:31:21,190 --> 00:31:22,670
Young Master and Old Madam will scold us.

516
00:31:22,670 --> 00:31:24,110
I'll give you a storybook.

517
00:31:24,110 --> 00:31:25,220
It's not about storybook.

518
00:31:25,220 --> 00:31:26,750
Two storytelling scripts.

519
00:31:27,130 --> 00:31:27,860
Young Madam.

520
00:31:27,870 --> 00:31:28,790
No matter how many storytelling scripts you give me, it's not okay.

521
00:31:28,790 --> 00:31:30,320
Ten storytelling scripts.

522
00:31:31,000 --> 00:31:32,400
Come out quickly.

523
00:31:37,450 --> 00:31:46,760
[Virtues Will Shine Forever]

524
00:31:58,060 --> 00:32:00,060
There are so many memorial tablets.

525
00:32:00,400 --> 00:32:02,470
That jade pendant is so important to him.

526
00:32:02,470 --> 00:32:04,800
Is it under his father's memorial tablet?

527
00:32:11,570 --> 00:32:12,330
[Memorial Tablet of My Ancestor, Xu Mingjiang]

528
00:32:12,350 --> 00:32:12,980
[Memorial Tablet of My Ancestor, Xu Zhengxiang]

529
00:32:16,240 --> 00:32:18,570
His father's memorial tablet isn't here?

530
00:32:24,110 --> 00:32:25,640
Ancestors of the Xu Family,

531
00:32:26,000 --> 00:32:26,890
sorry to offend you.

532
00:32:26,890 --> 00:32:28,020
Please understand.

533
00:32:30,750 --> 00:32:31,510
[Memorial Tablet of My Ancestor, Xu Changquan]

534
00:32:34,510 --> 00:32:35,880
[Memorial Tablet of My Ancestor, Xu Mingjiang]

535
00:33:25,830 --> 00:33:28,430
Memorial Tablet of My Late Father, Xu Chengsi.

536
00:33:28,780 --> 00:33:30,310
No wonder it's not outside.

537
00:33:30,310 --> 00:33:31,590
He hid it here.

538
00:33:53,060 --> 00:33:56,620
[There is a beast on the Jingyang Hill and it hurts people's lives. Please send hunters to kill it.]

539
00:34:02,470 --> 00:34:03,590
How childish.

540
00:34:42,790 --> 00:34:44,870
Why hasn't Young Madam come out yet?

541
00:34:45,230 --> 00:34:46,710
It's dark now.

542
00:34:49,840 --> 00:34:50,590
Xiao Qiu?

543
00:34:51,909 --> 00:34:52,630
Why are you here?

544
00:34:52,630 --> 00:34:53,400
Young Master.

545
00:34:53,400 --> 00:34:55,239
Shouldn't you be with Young Madam?

546
00:34:55,239 --> 00:34:56,100
Young Madam...

547
00:34:56,500 --> 00:34:58,430
Young Madam is not in the ancestral hall.

548
00:34:58,430 --> 00:35:01,360
She didn't ask me to guard the entrance here, either.

549
00:35:05,550 --> 00:35:08,950
Young Madam said that outsiders were not allowed to come inside,

550
00:35:08,950 --> 00:35:11,430
but Young Master is not an outsider.

551
00:35:20,680 --> 00:35:21,870
Who let you in?

552
00:35:24,800 --> 00:35:25,430
I...

553
00:35:25,450 --> 00:35:27,700
I just wanted to worship the ancestors.

554
00:35:27,840 --> 00:35:29,830
Then I walked inside here accidentally.

555
00:35:29,830 --> 00:35:32,560
Why are you holding my father's memorial tablet?

556
00:35:33,860 --> 00:35:35,590
I saw that it was a little dirty,

557
00:35:35,630 --> 00:35:36,910
so I wanted to clean it.

558
00:35:47,760 --> 00:35:49,030
Xu Muchen, let go of me!

559
00:35:49,150 --> 00:35:50,650
You didn't write "No entry".

560
00:35:50,650 --> 00:35:51,610
How would I know?

561
00:35:50,950 --> 00:35:53,260
[Inherit the Traditional Virtues]

562
00:35:52,270 --> 00:35:53,350
What are you doing?

563
00:35:53,350 --> 00:35:56,680
You're not allowed to step into the ancestral hall anymore.

564
00:35:57,680 --> 00:35:59,390
Why are you so furious?

565
00:36:04,950 --> 00:36:06,070
There must be

566
00:36:06,070 --> 00:36:07,550
a secret hidden there.

567
00:36:08,790 --> 00:36:09,310
Father,

568
00:36:11,320 --> 00:36:14,520
the woman who came here just now is the daughter of Duke Su.

569
00:36:14,980 --> 00:36:17,380
The reason why I didn't tell you previously

570
00:36:18,130 --> 00:36:20,590
is that I didn't know how to tell you about it.

571
00:36:22,380 --> 00:36:23,860
Because your case

572
00:36:25,480 --> 00:36:27,280
was handled by Duke Su back then.

573
00:36:28,140 --> 00:36:29,240
It's okay.

574
00:36:29,560 --> 00:36:30,470
Hurry up! Hurry up!

575
00:36:30,470 --> 00:36:31,190
Come here.

576
00:36:31,190 --> 00:36:31,750
Move them here now.

577
00:36:31,750 --> 00:36:32,510
Hurry!

578
00:36:37,340 --> 00:36:38,300
I didn't give up

579
00:36:38,300 --> 00:36:39,760
investigating your case.

580
00:36:41,590 --> 00:36:43,590
After all, a flaw can always be found

581
00:36:44,920 --> 00:36:46,520
even in the most perfect lie.

582
00:36:48,590 --> 00:36:50,930
I searched the ancestral hall so carefully,

583
00:36:50,930 --> 00:36:52,530
but I still couldn't find it.

584
00:36:53,710 --> 00:36:55,670
Where did he hide the jade pendant?

585
00:37:00,750 --> 00:37:01,610
Zhen?

586
00:37:02,000 --> 00:37:03,730
Why are you sitting here alone?

587
00:37:08,560 --> 00:37:10,160
Zhen, what's wrong with you?

588
00:37:10,390 --> 00:37:13,070
Did someone bully you, or did something wrong happen to you?

589
00:37:13,070 --> 00:37:13,670
I...

590
00:37:13,990 --> 00:37:16,710
When I passed by the ancestral hall just now,

591
00:37:16,920 --> 00:37:19,580
I wanted to go inside and worship the ancestors.

592
00:37:19,830 --> 00:37:21,760
Then Xu Muchen barged in,

593
00:37:21,890 --> 00:37:23,360
and he suddenly got furious.

594
00:37:23,360 --> 00:37:24,950
He pulled me out of the ancestral hall

595
00:37:24,950 --> 00:37:26,760
and even pushed me to the ground.

596
00:37:26,940 --> 00:37:28,740
He even pushed you to the ground?

597
00:37:29,870 --> 00:37:30,930
Xu Muchen was so rude.

598
00:37:30,930 --> 00:37:33,060
How could he treat his wife violently?

599
00:37:33,640 --> 00:37:35,590
Mother, don't be too angry.

600
00:37:35,990 --> 00:37:38,170
Maybe he was afraid that I would be clumsy

601
00:37:38,170 --> 00:37:40,270
and break my father-in-law's memorial tablet.

602
00:37:40,270 --> 00:37:42,530
Your father-in-law's memorial tablet?

603
00:37:43,100 --> 00:37:45,500
There's a small room in the ancestral hall.

604
00:37:45,600 --> 00:37:48,060
There's a memorial tablet in the small room.

605
00:37:49,360 --> 00:37:50,290
How ridiculous!

606
00:37:56,800 --> 00:37:58,930
As for this eldest daughter of Duke Su,

607
00:38:00,550 --> 00:38:02,010
I didn't want to marry her.

608
00:38:04,150 --> 00:38:06,610
But I couldn't disobey His Majesty's order.

609
00:38:07,670 --> 00:38:08,750
But don't worry.

610
00:38:09,840 --> 00:38:11,970
I will divorce her as soon as possible.

611
00:38:19,920 --> 00:38:20,580
Step aside.

612
00:38:22,230 --> 00:38:22,840
Mother.

613
00:38:23,180 --> 00:38:24,510
I told you to step aside.

614
00:38:34,600 --> 00:38:36,800
He only knows how to treat me violently.

615
00:38:37,760 --> 00:38:38,620
He deserves it.

616
00:38:41,840 --> 00:38:43,210
What did I tell you?

617
00:38:47,180 --> 00:38:49,510
I shouldn't worship my father privately.

618
00:38:50,510 --> 00:38:51,350
What else?

619
00:38:52,220 --> 00:38:54,500
I shouldn't investigate my father's case.

620
00:38:54,500 --> 00:38:56,160
Then what are these things?

621
00:38:57,450 --> 00:38:59,390
If I don't help my father clear his name,

622
00:38:59,390 --> 00:39:01,120
I'm not worthy of being his son.

623
00:39:07,540 --> 00:39:09,520
I told you not to investigate the case!

624
00:39:09,520 --> 00:39:10,190
Mother!

625
00:39:11,500 --> 00:39:12,960
Have you ever thought that

626
00:39:13,100 --> 00:39:15,060
if your father was really framed

627
00:39:15,090 --> 00:39:16,170
and died unjustly,

628
00:39:16,400 --> 00:39:17,620
how powerful the mastermind

629
00:39:17,620 --> 00:39:19,230
behind the conspiracy might be,

630
00:39:19,230 --> 00:39:21,630
and how dangerous your situation might be?

631
00:39:21,900 --> 00:39:22,890
I'm not afraid.

632
00:39:23,410 --> 00:39:24,500
You're not afraid?

633
00:39:25,100 --> 00:39:26,550
[Inherit the Traditional Virtues]

634
00:39:26,500 --> 00:39:27,360
Give them to me.

635
00:39:29,000 --> 00:39:30,770
[Inherit the Traditional Virtues]

636
00:39:29,090 --> 00:39:30,070
I am afraid.

637
00:39:36,260 --> 00:39:37,440
Do you know what I've been

638
00:39:37,440 --> 00:39:38,900
afraid of all these years?

639
00:39:40,190 --> 00:39:41,980
I was not afraid of you being naughty,

640
00:39:41,980 --> 00:39:43,810
I was not afraid of you ruining the reputation of our family.

641
00:39:43,810 --> 00:39:46,210
I was just afraid that you couldn't get out of your father's shadow

642
00:39:46,210 --> 00:39:49,120
and would always want to reverse the verdict for him.

643
00:39:49,120 --> 00:39:52,270
[Inherit the Traditional Virtues]

644
00:39:49,780 --> 00:39:51,240
Do you know how many people

645
00:39:51,620 --> 00:39:54,350
died in vain back then in order to reverse

646
00:39:54,470 --> 00:39:55,590
the verdict for your father?

647
00:39:55,590 --> 00:39:56,990
If anything wrong happens to you,

648
00:39:56,990 --> 00:39:58,750
how can I live?

649
00:40:00,070 --> 00:40:01,530
Since you're so stubborn,

650
00:40:01,590 --> 00:40:02,550
I'll burn it today.

651
00:40:02,550 --> 00:40:02,950
Mother!

652
00:40:02,950 --> 00:40:05,480
Then you won't think about this case anymore.

653
00:40:09,350 --> 00:40:10,530
[Inherit the Traditional Virtues]

654
00:40:14,600 --> 00:40:15,840
Put it inside.

655
00:40:17,280 --> 00:40:18,070
No.

656
00:40:19,560 --> 00:40:22,340
Put it inside!

657
00:40:22,340 --> 00:40:23,500
I'll say it again.

658
00:40:23,920 --> 00:40:25,260
Put it inside!

659
00:40:25,300 --> 00:40:27,110
Fire! Fire!

660
00:40:27,020 --> 00:40:28,070
[Inherit the Traditional Virtues]

661
00:40:29,900 --> 00:40:31,650
[Inherit the Traditional Virtues]

662
00:40:30,800 --> 00:40:31,730
Xu Muchen.

663
00:40:31,750 --> 00:40:33,040
Why are you burning things here?

664
00:40:33,040 --> 00:40:35,100
Didn't you know how dangerous it was?

665
00:40:42,670 --> 00:40:43,270
Mother.

666
00:40:45,400 --> 00:40:46,870
Why are you angry?

667
00:40:47,590 --> 00:40:48,920
Is it because my husband

668
00:40:48,930 --> 00:40:50,790
treated me so violently just now?

669
00:40:51,590 --> 00:40:53,470
Actually, it was mainly my fault.

670
00:40:53,490 --> 00:40:55,120
I shouldn't have barged into the ancestral hall

671
00:40:55,120 --> 00:40:56,320
without permission.

672
00:40:56,880 --> 00:40:58,180
I won't do it again.

673
00:40:58,590 --> 00:40:59,720
As a family,

674
00:40:59,720 --> 00:41:01,070
we should talk and discuss things patiently

675
00:41:01,070 --> 00:41:02,110
from now on.

676
00:41:07,590 --> 00:41:08,590
Xu Muchen.

677
00:41:10,070 --> 00:41:11,590
Behave yourself.

678
00:41:14,910 --> 00:41:15,590
Zhen.

679
00:41:16,070 --> 00:41:17,170
Help me back to my room.

680
00:41:17,170 --> 00:41:22,970
[Inherit the Traditional Virtues]

681
00:41:32,690 --> 00:41:39,140
[Wedding]

682
00:41:42,350 --> 00:41:43,340
Today,

683
00:41:43,440 --> 00:41:44,750
I didn't find the jade pendant,

684
00:41:44,750 --> 00:41:46,230
but I'm quite exhausted instead.

685
00:41:46,230 --> 00:41:53,930
[Wedding]

686
00:42:02,260 --> 00:42:07,260
[Wedding]

687
00:42:11,940 --> 00:42:14,150
It looks like he really loves his father,

688
00:42:14,150 --> 00:42:15,680
who was a corrupt official.

689
00:42:21,550 --> 00:42:24,550
Why is it different from what my master has described?

690
00:42:25,560 --> 00:42:27,760
Didn't you treat the wound on your hand?

691
00:42:29,130 --> 00:42:29,860
I'm fine.

692
00:42:32,210 --> 00:42:33,250
Let me get you some medicine.

693
00:42:33,110 --> 00:42:40,980
[Wedding]

694
00:42:42,390 --> 00:42:43,950
Do you need me to apply the medicine to your wound?

695
00:42:43,950 --> 00:42:44,950
Just give it to me.

696
00:42:48,190 --> 00:42:50,390
How come you know where the medicine is?

697
00:42:51,410 --> 00:42:52,110
I...

698
00:42:54,080 --> 00:42:55,140
-I...
-Thank you

699
00:42:55,950 --> 00:42:57,080
for your help today.

700
00:42:59,040 --> 00:43:00,610
Darling, you don't need to thank me.

701
00:43:00,610 --> 00:43:02,420
This is what I should do.

702
00:43:02,440 --> 00:43:03,310
Wait a moment.

703
00:43:03,340 --> 00:43:04,670
I'll get you some water.

704
00:43:08,310 --> 00:43:10,520
It was my fault for treating you violently today.

705
00:43:10,520 --> 00:43:13,010
Actually, it was also my fault.

706
00:43:13,210 --> 00:43:14,070
I shouldn't have

707
00:43:14,070 --> 00:43:15,710
worshiped the ancestors

708
00:43:15,710 --> 00:43:17,170
without your permission.

709
00:43:21,710 --> 00:43:23,640
Yesterday, I already told you that

710
00:43:23,650 --> 00:43:24,980
we were not a good match.

711
00:43:25,420 --> 00:43:26,780
Why don't we get divorced as soon as possible?

712
00:43:26,780 --> 00:43:27,290
No.

